These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, hiking
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, pilot
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, motorbike
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the accountant is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | hiking       | woodworking |
| Job         | pilot | accountant  |
| Sport       | sailing    | handball    |
| Transport   | motorbike       | trike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, dancer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the security-guard is on the far left##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | 7up |
| Job           | security-guard | dancer      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | western      |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | weightlifting     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, hip-hop
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, bike
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | almond-milk  |
| Food          | broccoli    | kiwi   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | punk   |
| Transport     | bike     | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
