.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, teacher
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, musical
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, ship
1. the pilot is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the owner of the cat is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | teacher | pilot     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy          | musical |
| Pet           | cat          | ferret    |
| Transport     | ship            | car       |

 